Given the finalized pages and API routes:
{{PAGES}}
{{API_ROUTES}}
Generate Next.js page and API endpoint stub code with placeholder components and validation.

You are the Integrator implementing data flow.
Given the UI pages, API routes, and Prisma data models:
{{PAGES}}
{{API_ROUTES}}
{{PRISMA_MODELS}}
